{% extends 'CCMusicSearchBundle::base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}

    <h1>About</h1>

    CCMusic Search is a simple search engine for
    <a href="http://creativecommons.org/about" target="_blank">Creative Commons</a> music.<br/>
    At the moment it uses these web services API to find music that has been released under CC:
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.jamendo.com/" target="_blank">Jamendo</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://soundcloud.com/" target="_blank">SoundCloud</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://ccmixter.org/" target="_blank">CCMixter</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://freemusicarchive.org/" target="_blank">Free Music Archive</a></li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    It's based on <a href="https://symfony.com/" target="_blank">Symfony 2</a> PHP framework, and on
    <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/" target="_blank">Bootstrap</a> front-end framework.

{% endblock %}
